OL,5,CIF ASKED FOR A DANCE...       Q(.,.#   
OL,7, If you're just about to jet off to     
OL,8, sunnier climes for aCsultry summer     
OL,9,Choliday,Gbe wary of locals who         
OL,10, proposition you for a dance...         
OL,12, "While there's nought wrong with you   
OL,13, having a boogie, there is if the boogie
OL,14, you're about to encounter is with      
OL,15, bears," saysCJonathan OwenGof theCWorld
OL,16,CSociety for the Protection of Animals. 
OL,18, "Stick to your guns andCsay no.GIt's   
OL,19, a cruel attraction which you can stop!"
