OL,5,CIF ASKED FOR A DANCE...       Q(.,.#   
OL,7, For centuriesCman has exploited bears, 
OL,8, says expert Jonathan Owen.             
OL,10, "At one time, dancing brown bears      
OL,11, were common exhibits in countries      
OL,12, all over the world but now they are    
OL,13, confined to countries likeCIndia,      
OL,14,CTurkey, Greece, BulgariaGandCHungary.  
OL,16,C"TouristsGare to blame for its         
OL,17, continued existence - therefore only   
OL,18, tourists can determine its end once and
OL,19, for all," he adds.                     
