OL,5,CIF ASKED FOR A DANCE...       Q(.,.#   
OL,7, Bear dancing is recognised as cruel in 
OL,8, Turkey and as a result it is banned,   
OL,9, says an official from theCTurkish      
OL,10,CEmbassyGin London.                     
OL,12, She adds: "Anyone caught parading      
OL,13, dancing bears will be prosecuted       
OL,14, -Cit is a serious offence."            
OL,16, TheCGreek, Bulgarian, IndianGand       
OL,17,CHungarianGEmbassies in London were     
OL,18, unable to offer a comment.             
